package com.kml.github.kemoleseding.objModules

import com.kml.github.kemoleseding.R

class CoCardEntry(
    val coPic: Int,
    val coName: String,
    val coDescENG: String,
    val coDescSETS: String
)

val tbc = CoCardEntry(
    coPic = R.drawable.tbclogo,
    coName = "Thusang Bana Centre",
    coDescENG = "     Thusang Bana Centre (TBC) is a community voluntary based nonprofit making organization in Molepolole with the mandate of caring for orphans & vulnerable children. Their health educators work to destigmatize HIV and AIDS in the Kweneng district and beyond. \n\n     TBC's founder Stanley Monageng is a tireless advocate and Treat All Champion. The film Ke mo Leseding follows Stanley Monageng as he undertakes a 400-kilometer trek throughout Botswana to raise awareness of HIV treatment, and destigmatize HIV and AIDS, and educate Batswana on the latest treatment for the disease.",
    coDescSETS = "     Thusang Bana Centre(TBC) ke lekalana/mokgatlho la boithapo le le sa direng dipoelo mo motseng wa Molepolole. Boikarabelo ja lone ke go tlhokomela bana ba dikhutsana le bao mo diphatseng tsa go tsuulolwa. \n" +
            "Mokgatlho ona le badiri ba ba rutang ka tsa botsogo mme ba remeletse thata mo go ruteng sechaba go ema kgatlhanong le go kgetholola batho mabapi le seemo sa bone sa mogare wa HIV le bolwetse jwa AIDS. Setlhopha se se tsaya karolo mo go ruteng sechaba sa Botswana so tlhe, mme remeletse thata mo kgaolong ya Kweneng.\n" +
            "Mokgatlho o o simolotswe ke rre Stanley Monageng, yo osa iponeng tsapa go buelela dikgang tsa botsogo, ebile ele morotloetsimogolo wa lenaneo la gore mongwe le mongwe yo o tshelang ka mogare wa HIV a tsenngwe mo lenaneong la diritibatse(Treat All Champion). \n" +
            "Mo maitekong a gagwe, ke ka moo ba diri ba setshwantsho sa motshikhinyego sa Ke-mo-Leseding ba latedisang mosepele wa gagwe wa 400km go ralala lehatshe la Botswana a tsibosa le go ruta sechaba ka kalafi ya HIV le go emisa kgethololo mo go bao ba ba tshelang ka mogare wa HIV le AIDS. Godimo ga moo o ruta sechaba ka mananeo a masha a kalafi ya bolwetse jo. \n"
)

val pc = CoCardEntry(
    coPic = R.drawable.pclogoonly,
    coName = "Peace Corps Botswana",
    coDescENG = "     Peace Corps Botswana assisted in the production of Ke mo Leseding and aided Thusang Bana Centre with the distribution of the film and its curriculum. Both during and after COVID-19 evacuated the volunteers, Peace Corps continued to work with Thusang Bana Centre to bring Ke mo Leseding to Batswana.\n\n     Paul O'Brien and Isaac Devoid supported Thusang Bana Centre and Stanley Monageng during the 12 days that make up the bulk of the footage used to create Ke mo Leseding. Both are now RPCVs - Returned Peace Corps Volunteers - but continue to develop Ke mo Leseding because of TBC's inspiring message and Stanley's tireless commitment.",
    coDescSETS = "     Paul O'Brien le Isaac Devoid bane ba eme Thusang Bana Centre le Stanley Monageng mo malatsing a lesome le bobedi(12) a go dira motheo wa setshwantsho sa Ke-mo-Leseding. Ba botlhe ke ba ba Baithaopi ba ba boetseng kwa gabone, mme ba tsweletse ka go netefatsa ha setshwantsho se se dirwa. Ba dira se ka go rotloediwa ke molaetsa le maikaelelo a a tsepameng a mokgatlho wa TBC le go sa iponeng tsapa ga ga rre Monageng."
)